Frank Drebin is persuaded out of retirement to go undercover in a
state prison. There he is to find out what top terrorist, Rocco,
has planned for when he escapes. Frank's wife, Jane, is desperate
for a baby.. this adds to Frank's problems. A host of celebrities
at the Academy awards ceremony are humiliated by Frank as he blunders
his way trying to foil Rocco.
